headline: Is United Parcel Service Stock a Buy Now?
summary: At its current share price, UPS has a 6.5% dividend yield.  UPS is overhauling its business to focus on its most profitable customers.  United Parcel Service (NYSE: UPS) is in the middle of a major corporate overhaul.
